body.description: Feel your fresh with Glade PlugIns Scented Oil Air Freshener Refills with Orchid & Neroli scents, a vibrant, fresh floral blend that awakens the beauty and optimism we can find in everyday moments. Transform the energy in your home when you use Orchid & Neroli fragrance oils made without phthalates, parabens, formaldehydes or nitro musks. You'll enjoy the bold aromas of delicate neroli petals and blooming orchid. The Glade Fresh collection uses multidimensional, artfully layered scents to bring you a fresh, new experience. Use these Glade refills in any Glade PlugIns scented oil warmer and infuse different-sized rooms with continuous, long-lasting fragrance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely Floral Scent
reviews.reviewText: This two pack of Orchid & Neroli plugins is absolutely lovey. It is a floral scent that is strong, but it isn't overbearing. I have. a room that is about 400 square feet and it fills the room up with scent very well. It isn't a light scent, but rather a sharp, sweet scent, that is also fresh. I've had it plugged in for about a week on the medium setting and it as just as strong as the first day. I would get this scent over and over again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super pretty smell
reviews.reviewText: I really love the scent of this particular one. It's so light and floral. It smells like an early spring day. I will say to make sure that you have the proper warmer for this to go in to though, because it won't fit in the original one I was hoping to put it in. I ended up having to use a white plastic one at my office instead of the pretty one my husband got me for the house. You definitely can't go wrong with this scent though. It's definitely noticeable without being overpowering. I just wish I'd gotten this in a bigger pack!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not My Favorite Scent
reviews.reviewText: This plug-in works well, so that's not an issue, but I find this particular fragrance to be a bit "sharp" on the nose. I placed it in my bedroom at first but had to move it so I could sleep. Just too strong for my liking.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lovely floral scent
reviews.reviewText: These two glade plugins are delightful, with a beautiful floral scent that lasts a long time. The Glade brand is a solid one, and my original plugin oil warmer has been working for close to a decade. They're really reliable and at a great price. This set is wonderful, but the price is higher than the pair of refills in my local grocery store; so, unless you're looking for this specific scent, that might be a better value. I'm a big fan of the Glade brand and I'd recommend this scent for anyone who enjoys a floral scent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Keeps the Laundry Room with Litter Box Smelling Fresh
reviews.reviewText: Using this Orchid & Neroli scent refill in our laundry room which also houses the litter box for our two cats. Yep, that room gets stinky, but this Glade refill is doing a great job keeping the room fresh smelling with a pleasant floral scent. It's a pretty strong scent and we are able to keep the unit set to lowest setting and still works well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great But Strong Smell
reviews.reviewText: My current plugin refill was almost used up, so I decided to give this scent a try. I didn't have any trouble using it with my plugin, and it does smell really nice. My only issue is that it's a bit too strong for my nose, so I don't think I'll use it too often.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Glade Plug In Refills Orchid and Neroli
reviews.reviewText: Glad brand is well known, and it has never let me down. The quality is great as expected BUT what I found out this time, that I had never noticed before is what this product is free from. This product is made without: PHTHALATES, PARABENS, FORMALDEHYDES, and NITRO MUSKS! I usually only use these Glade plug ins when I have visitors because I thought they weren't super healthy but now, I feel safer using them more often.
